<br>
46-48 quad dorfs in Butcherblock. Go to the camp near the shore (not the docks). Den Ironblend and friends. Pull Den, run near the house to the left (when facing away from the shore) Do not run into it, you won't have enough time. Run right by the side of the outer wall. Do two laps around the house. (They should now be bunched up) Get your distance, and BoF. Then just use Circle of Force to kill them.<br>
<br>
At 48 (If you have a decent amount of mana) head to TD, and quad Spirocs. At 49 I went there (click my sig to see my int/mana) I was able to quad any spiroc there. It would take all my mana, and if there were too many resists, I would need to harvest. <br>
<br>
